OL,3,CLower standing charge tariffs set to
OL,4,Cbe available by end of January, says
OL,5,COfgem
OL,7,FEnergy suppliers will be made to offer
OL,8,Fat least one tariff with lower
OL,9,Fstanding charges as soon as January
OL,10,Funder plans confirmed by the industry
OL,11,Fregulator, but it ditched proposals to
OL,12,Fremove the fixed costs entirely for
OL,13,Fsome deals.
OL,15,FOfgem said it wants to give consumers
OL,16,Fmore choice on how they pay standing
OL,17,Fcharges, with the plans set to allow
OL,18,Fhouseholds to pay the costs as part of
OL,19,Ftheir unit rate by lowering the daily
OL,20,Ffixed amount.
