OL,3,CLower standing charge tariffs set to
OL,4,Cbe available by end of January, says
OL,5,COfgem
OL,7,FIf given the go-ahead, the new tariffs
OL,8,Fcould be available by the end of
OL,9,FJanuary.
OL,11,FStanding charges are applied daily,
OL,12,Fregardless of how much energy the
OL,13,Fcustomer uses, and are used to cover
OL,14,Fthe cost of supplying energy to homes
OL,15,Fand businesses.
OL,17,FThey also cover the costs of building
OL,18,Fnew network infrastructure and keeping
OL,19,Fthe power on when energy suppliers go
OL,20,Fbust.
