OL,5,COfgem
OL,7,FCampaigners say they are unfair
OL,8,Fbecause everybody pays the same rate,
OL,9,Fmeaning they make up a far higher
OL,10,Fproportion of bills for people using
OL,11,Fless energy.
OL,13,FOfgem stressed these charges cannot be
OL,14,Fremoved entirely and that they can
OL,15,Fonly be moved from one part of the
OL,16,Fbill to another, which means they are
OL,17,Funlikely to mean lower energy costs.
