OL,3,CLower standing charge tariffs set to
OL,4,Cbe available by end of January, says
OL,5,COfgem
OL,7,FIt said it dropped earlier plans for
OL,8,Ftariffs with zero standing charges and
OL,9,Fmuch higher unit rates, as this could
OL,10,Fhave unfairly impacted consumers with
OL,11,Fhigh energy needs, such as those who
OL,12,Frely on power for medical reasons.
OL,14,FIt is also looking to introduce a
OL,15,Fminimum usage on to the new tariffs so
OL,16,Fthat those with second homes or
OL,17,Fproperties left vacant for long
OL,18,Fperiods do not disproportionately
OL,19,Fbenefit.
