OL,3,CLower standing charge tariffs set to
OL,4,Cbe available by end of January, says
OL,5,COfgem
OL,7,FOfgem is now launching one final
OL,8,Fconsultation on the plans, with aims
OL,9,Fto make a decision by the end of the
OL,10,Fyear, paving the way for the new
OL,11,Ftariffs to be available to everyone
OL,12,Facross Britain by the end of January.
OL,14,FTim Jarvis, director general of
OL,15,Fmarkets at Ofgem, said: "We've
OL,16,Flistened to thousands of consumers
OL,17,Fthat wanted to see changes to the
OL,18,Fstanding charge and taken action.
