OL,3,CLower standing charge tariffs set to
OL,4,Cbe available by end of January, says
OL,5,COfgem
OL,7,F"We have carefully considered how we
OL,8,Fcan offer more choice on how they pay
OL,9,Fthese fixed costs, however we have
OL,10,Ftaken care to ensure we don't make
OL,11,Fsome customers worse off.
OL,13,F"After examining all the options
OL,14,Favailable to us, we believe that the
OL,15,Fright way forward is to require all
OL,16,Fmajor suppliers to offer at least one
OL,17,Ftariff with a lower standing charge.
