OL,3,CLower standing charge tariffs set to
OL,4,Cbe available by end of January, says
OL,5,COfgem
OL,7,F"This will deliver the choice we know
OL,8,Fcustomers want, without having a
OL,9,Fdetrimental impact on customers that
OL,10,Fhave high energy needs."
OL,12,FBut he added: "We cannot remove these
OL,13,Fcharges, we can only move costs around.
OL,15,F"These changes would give households
OL,16,Fthe choice they have asked for, but
OL,17,Fit's important that everyone carefully
OL,18,Fconsiders what's right for them as
OL,19,Fthese tariffs are unlikely to reduce
OL,20,Fbills on their own."
