OL,3,CLower standing charge tariffs set to
OL,4,Cbe available by end of January, says
OL,5,COfgem
OL,7,FIt comes ahead of a 2% rise in energy
OL,8,Fcosts when the next price cap change
OL,9,Ftakes effect on October 1, which will
OL,10,Fsee the bill for a typical household
OL,11,Frise from #1,720 to #1,755 a year.
OL,13,FMartin McCluskey, minister for energy
OL,14,Fconsumers, said: "Consumers should
OL,15,Fhave freedom and choice when choosing
OL,16,Fan energy tariff that works for them.
OL,18,F"This proposal will make more tariffs
OL,19,Favailable on the market, giving people
OL,20,Fmore options to pay lower standing
OL,21,Fcharges if that suits their needs."
