OL,5,COfgem
OL,7,FOfgem said the new lower standing
OL,8,Fcharge tariff mandate would be likely
OL,9,Fto only be a short-term measure while
OL,10,Fit moots permanent changes to allocate
OL,11,Fcosts within the system, as the UK
OL,12,Fshifts towards renewable energy.
OL,14,FSimon Francis, co-ordinator of the End
OL,15,FFuel Poverty Coalition, said it was a
OL,16,F"small step forward" and called on the
OL,17,Findustry to make sure that households
OL,18,F"properly understand the deals they
OL,19,Fare signing up for".
